        ne peut garantir l'absence totale d’erreurs ou d’interruptions techniques.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .legal-page { padding: 120px 0; }
    .container-legal {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 32px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--kano-light);
    }
    h1, h2 {
      font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;
      color: #fff;
    }
    h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); margin-bottom: 40px; }
    h2 { margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.4rem; }
    p { opacity: .85; }
    @media(max-width:768px){
      .container-legal{ padding: 0 20px; }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>